### ===============================
### CAMPAIGNS
### ===============================

@token = SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
@linkedinAccountId = 
@campaignId = 

### Criar Campanha
POST http://localhost:3001/api/campaigns
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Campanha de Desenvolvedores SP",
  "linkedin_account_id": "{{linkedinAccountId}}",
  "industry": "Tecnologia",
  "location": "São Paulo, Brasil",
  "target_titles": ["Software Developer", "Full Stack Developer", "Backend Developer"],
  "target_keywords": ["JavaScript", "Node.js", "React"],
  "template_message": "Olá {name}! Vi seu perfil e gostaria de me conectar. Estou recrutando desenvolvedores talentosos.",
  "daily_limit": 50
}

### Listar Campanhas
GET http://localhost:3001/api/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar Campanhas Ativas
GET http://localhost:3001/api/campaigns?status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obter Campanha Específica
GET http://localhost:3001/api/campaigns/{{campaignId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar Campanha
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/campaigns/{{campaignId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Campanha Atualizada",
  "daily_limit": 100
}

### Iniciar Campanha
POST http://localhost:3001/api/campaigns/{{campaignId}}/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Pausar Campanha
POST http://localhost:3001/api/campaigns/{{campaignId}}/pause
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obter Estatísticas
GET http://localhost:3001/api/campaigns/{{campaignId}}/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Deletar Campanha
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/campaigns/{{campaignId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}